Map AIM_BRIDGE
Version 1.0 - Beta

Hello, This is My First map for CS:S.
I know This Map isn't Very Complex and Big, But It's Funny. and a Perfect map for Snipers :)
This is My First Map, So Excuse me if It's Not very Complex. Also Feel Free to Vote and Post!

(I also Like to See this Map in a Server :D)

Installation:
Simply Extract the cstrike Folder to your Counter-Strike: Source Directory. (e.g. D:\Games\CSS)

Features:
Working Cubemaps for Both LDR and HDR.
Optimized Map using Nodraws.
Containing a Few Physics Objects. (Like Explosive Barrel, etc...)
